{"abstract":"The paper presents an approach to the problem of controlling the configuration of a team of mobile agents equipped with cameras so as to optimize the quality of the estimates derived from their measurements. The issue of optimizing the robots' configuration is particularly important in the context of teams equipped with vision sensors since most estimation schemes of interest will involve some form of triangulation. We provide a theoretical framework for tackling the sensor planning problem and a practical computational strategy, inspired by work on particle filtering, for implementing the approach. The ideas have been demonstrated both in simulation and on actual robotic platforms. The results indicate that the framework is able to solve fairly difficult sensor planning problems online without requiring excessive amounts of computational resources.","arxivId":null,"authors":[{"authorId":"1772013","name":"J. Spletzer","url":"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/1772013"},{"authorId":"31589308","name":"C. J. Taylor","url":"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/31589308"}],"citationVelocity":0,"citations":[{"arxivId":null,"authors":[{"authorId":"2115922855","name":"Ju Wang"},{"authorId":"107927179","name":"Sagar P. Pundit"},{"authorId":"40324487","name":"Ahmed F. Abdelzaher"},{"authorId":"2056022116","name":"Melissa Watts"}],"doi":"10.1109/MIPR.2019.00063","intent":["background"],"isInfluential":false,"paperId":"6811a0912257b6b4e382e852cbe414b57d011069","title":"Asynchronous Localization of Ground Objects Using a 2-UAV System","url":"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/6811a0912257b6b4e382e852cbe414b57d011069","venue":"2019 IEEE Conference on Multimedia Information Processing and Retrieval (MIPR)","year":2019},{"arxivId":null,"authors":[{"authorId":"2071086349","name":"Declan O'Beirne"}],"doi":null,"intent":["background"],"isInfluential":false,"paperId":"e033cc5743673e59c7a99b7f0c19f3e9aa69eabd","title":"A market framework for collaborative robot exp